PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776715554
OL,3,CNew sighting reported of missing
OL,4,Ccapybara who escaped from zoo
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Ms Nyman
OL,7,Fsaid: "I saw something run across the
OL,8,Froad, and I immediately thought, oh my
OL,9,Fgosh, it's a capybara.
OL,11,F"So I quickly pulled in and jumped out
OL,12,Fmy car, left my daughter in the car,
OL,13,Fand rushed to go and try and get a
OL,14,Fphotograph of it, and it kind of
OL,15,Flooked at me in the field and then ran
OL,16,Faway quite quickly.
OL,18,FShe continued: "I immediately thought
OL,19,Fit was the capybara, and then I sort
OL,20,Fof second-guessed myself thinking, was
OL,21,Fit a dog? Was it a small deer?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776715554
OL,3,CNew sighting reported of missing
OL,4,Ccapybara who escaped from zoo
OL,6,F"And then I kind of was looking at the
OL,7,Fstature of the small legs, the round
OL,8,Fbottom, and thought, no, it's
OL,9,Fdefinitely nothing like a dog or a
OL,10,Fdeer, and it was completely alone, and
OL,11,Fit was quite skittish, and I was
OL,12,Fexpecting that from a capybara."
OL,14,FIn a statement, Marwell Zoo said: "The
OL,15,Fteams are continuing to use the same
OL,16,Fmethods of trying to track Samba down
OL,17,Fincluding camera traps, thermal drones
OL,18,Fand a specialist dog unit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776715554
OL,3,CNew sighting reported of missing
OL,4,Ccapybara who escaped from zoo
OL,6,F"The continued request is for the
OL,7,Fpublic to call the hotline, 07436
OL,8,F167401, with any sightings and an
OL,9,Fexact location."
OL,11,FSamba escaped from a temporary holding
OL,12,Fenclosure at Marwell Zoo near
OL,13,FWinchester on Tuesday 17th March.
OL,15,FHer sister, Tango, also ran off but
OL,16,Fkeepers were quickly able to locate
OL,17,Fand re-capture her.
OL,19,FThe pair had recently arrived from
OL,20,FJimmy's Farm & Wildlife Park in
OL,21,FSuffolk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
